Variables:

var userChoices
var userGuess
var wins
var losses
var remainingGuesses



Steps:

1. Resets page
2. Computer chooses random word from array
3. Computer matches length of word with spaces
4. User presses key
5. CPU checks for duplicate entry
6. CPU matches key with letters in chosen word
7. If yes, reveal letter and placement
8. If no, reduce available guesses by one
9. Show image
9. Add +1 to wins if user guesses word
10. Add +1 to losses if users guesses reach 0
11. Reset page